-more -->\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Arnaud Broes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2092:\"<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-2407 aligncenter\" src=\"http://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site.jpg\" alt=\"Not sure how to generate organic visitors? We\'ve listed 10 methods to drive traffic to your WordPress website.\" width=\"850\" height=\"250\" srcset=\"https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site.jpg 850w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-300x88.jpg 300w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-768x226.jpg 768w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-100x29.jpg 100w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-150x44.jpg 150w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-200x59.jpg 200w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-450x132.jpg 450w, https://semperplugins.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drive-Traffic-to-Your-WordPress-Site-600x176.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" /></p>\n<p>Your website rocks. So do your products and services. You constantly produce great and valuable content. Problem is, no one is reading it and your web traffic is slowing down or even non-existent.</p>\n<p>A consistent flow of traffic is vital to the success and survival of your site. You’ve probably read numerous articles and taken some courses to discover the best and most effective ways to drive traffic to your site. But then you ran into another problem: those tips and tactics are already used by a majority of sites. So now you’re on the hunt for more creative ways to stand out and get more relevant traffic.</p>\n<p>You’re in the right place. We&#8217;ve gathered ten unique and effective ways to drive valuable traffic to your website. Let’s first review a few of the essential common tactics before we dive into some other creative and fun marketing strategies.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://semperplugins.com/methods-to-generate-organic-traffic/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"12\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Comprehensive SEO Checklist for 2016\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"https://semperplugins.com/seo-checklist-2016/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://semperplugins.com/seo-checklist-2016/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_l